column5: Just finished this...  January 2007 MuskieQuest Newsleter  and don't forget to visit the main page for another shot at the Esox Angler Contest....
That's a nice simple artical,I like it. You usually read a bunch of articals that contradict each other and you just end up being confused, lol.
Now we just need muskie season to open up. Only 6 more months to go
